Newest Filings











Wesley Chapel Hospitality Investment Fund LP $5,000,000 Financing
Wesley Chapel Hospitality Investment Fund LP just submitted form D announcing $5,000,000 financing.  This is a new filing. Wesley Chapel Hospitality Investment Fund LP was able to sell $1,000,000. That is 20% of the round of financing. The total private offering amount was $5,000,000. The financing was made by 2 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $500,000. The financing document was filed on 2016-10-17. Wesley Chapel Hospitality Investment Fund LP is based in  303 SW 8TH STREET, SUITE 1  OCALA 34471. The firm's business is Pooled Investment Fund. The form was signed by  Vijay Patel.





